          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h1>Shipping Policy</h1><h2>Processing & Delivery</h2><p>At ROCKALS, we ensure your order reaches you swiftly and securely. Here's what you need to know:</p><ul><li><strong>Order Processing:</strong> All orders are processed within 1–2 business days of confirmation.</li><li><strong>Delivery Timeline:</strong> Standard delivery takes 5 to 7 business days across India.</li><li><strong>Tracking:</strong> You'll receive tracking details via SMS, WhatsApp, or Email immediately after dispatch.</li></ul><h3>Shipping Options & Costs</h3><ul><li><strong>Free Shipping:</strong> Complimentary shipping on all prepaid orders across India.</li><li><strong>Cash on Delivery (COD):</strong> Available on eligible orders with a handling fee applied at checkout.</li></ul><h3>Important Conditions</h3><p>Please note the following to ensure smooth delivery:</p><ul><li><strong>Accurate Information:</strong> Provide complete and correct shipping details. ROCKALS is not responsible for delivery issues caused by incomplete or incorrect information.</li><li><strong>Delivery Delays:</strong> Timelines may vary due to courier delays, weather, or unforeseen circumstances. ROCKALS is not liable for delays caused by third-party logistics providers.</li><li><strong>Failed Delivery Attempts:</strong> If delivery fails due to customer unavailability, redelivery charges may apply and will be communicated to you in advance.</li></ul><h3>Order Modifications & Cancellations</h3><ul><li><strong>Modification Window:</strong> Orders can be cancelled or modified within 2 hours of placement by contacting our customer support team.</li><li><strong>Post-Dispatch:</strong> Once your order has been dispatched, it cannot be cancelled or modified.</li></ul><h3>Need Help?</h3><p>For any questions about your shipment or to make changes to your order, please reach out to our customer support team within 2 hours of placing your order. We're here to help ensure your ROCKALS experience is exceptional.</p>"
